"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月20日消息，桥水基金创始人RayDalio表示，现金是最糟糕的投资，因为会被通货膨胀蚕食。他透露，[加密货币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)是他投资组合的一部分，并将加密货币视为“在现金价值实际贬值的环境中的替代货币”。（bitcoin）\",\"timestamp\":1639995933,\"title\":\"桥水基金创始人：加密货币是他投资组合的一部分\"},\"digest\":\"_M89aBghsQbDanFuNGUGa7DzmSxl0uX6TckbLbXdOtk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xEa38a42bD8CB5fCA6Bd87fA745f059ADD2bE64bF\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Sk5ZrT8Yl877Px0fCKVH7c7f4zSQoe2t0oO3IU-mqeU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"1jBxwisvJaVKSqj7KKdpKN_FN3dadYzqSmWekKhyjgg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Mgdoedl-pYzdiAlyqJ5W0oM4NaPM_kMti1vLK83RVgv2gUgAhEvl0r48ytcouucrkUuYu5h_1vS_94OBKH4-9Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x116861ee27fb2cea8ce08ab7fffa369f388c7791a247fcafd1a2a199e6a7963e5ed73965595f3d9c14179842a34f8b62b8703a8cf583117f821b579f90477d671c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Sk5ZrT8Yl877Px0fCKVH7c7f4zSQoe2t0oO3IU-mqeU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"1jBxwisvJaVKSqj7KKdpKN_FN3dadYzqSmWekKhyjgg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"_M89aBghsQbDanFuNGUGa7DzmSxl0uX6TckbLbXdOtk\"}"